## PROJECT STRUCTURE

```
src/
├── components/
│   ├── ui/              # Atomic reusable components (Button, Badge, Card, etc.)
│   ├── sections/        # Portfolio sections (Hero, About, Skills, Experience, etc.)
│   └── layout/          # Header, Footer, Navigation
├── layouts/
│   └── BaseLayout.astro # Main layout with full SEO setup
├── pages/
│   ├── index.astro
│   ├── projects/
│   │   └── [slug].astro # Dynamic project pages
│   └── 404.astro
├── content/
│   ├── config.ts        # Content Collections schema (for MDX project details)
│   └── projects/        # Optional MDX files for long-form project case studies
├── data/                # JSON data source (current)
├── lib/
│   ├── data/            # Data service layer (abstraction over JSON / future API)
│   └── utils.ts         # Helpers, formatters, cn() utility
├── types/
│   └── index.ts         # All TypeScript interfaces and types
├── styles/
│   └── global.css       # CSS variables, reset, base styles, fluid typography
└── public/
    ├── robots.txt
    ├── favicon.svg
    ├── apple-touch-icon.png
    └── site.webmanifest
```

